title: Deltaisos for Fedora 14 Final TC1 -> RC1 i386
description:
Deltaisos to generate the entire Fedora 14 Final RC1 i386 install disc set. First use Fedora-14-Final.TC1_RC1-i386-DVD.diso to convert from the Final TC1 i386 DVD to the Final RC1 i386 DVD.  Then use the other deltaisos to convert from the new DVD image to each of the other new install images.

Instructions at https://fedoraproject.org/wiki/Delta_ISOs
